{"name": "missing", "metadata": {"name": "Missing", "version": "5.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 6 - Mature", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Zope :: 5", "License :: OSI Approved :: Zope Public License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": "https://github.com/zopefoundation/Missing", "license": "ZPL 2.1", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["ExtensionClass", "zope.deferredimport"], "summary": "Special Missing objects used in Zope.", "upload_time": 1687328394}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://github.com/zopefoundation/Missing/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg\n:target: https://github.com/zopefoundation/Missing/actions/workflows/tests.yml\n```\n\n```{image} https://coveralls.io/repos/github/zopefoundation/Missing/badge.svg?branch=master\n:target: https://coveralls.io/github/zopefoundation/Missing?branch=master\n```\n\n```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/Missing.svg\n:alt: Current version on PyPI\n:target: https://pypi.org/project/Missing/\n```\n\n```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/Missing.svg\n:alt: Supported Python versions\n:target: https://pypi.org/project/Missing/\n```\n\n# Missing\n\nMissing provides special objects used in some Zope internals like the ZCatalog.\n\n# Changelog\n\n## 5.0 (2023-06-21)\n\n- Drop support for Python 2.7, 3.5, 3.6.\n- Deprecate `._Missing` which containes just BBB imports.\n\n## 4.2 (2022-11-16)\n\n- Add support for Python 3.8, 3.9, 3.10, 3.11\n\n## 4.1 (2018-10-05)\n\n- Drop support for Python 3.4.\n- Add support for Python 3.7.\n\n## 4.0.1 (2017-08-25)\n\n- Restore `Missing._Missing` module for pickle compatibility with the old\n  C extension version. \\[<https://github.com/zopefoundation/Missing/issues/3>\\]\n\n## 4.0 (2017-05-16)\n\n- Add support for bytes and matrix multiplication.\n- Remove the Python 2-only C extension.\n\n## 3.2 (2017-04-26)\n\n- Add support for Python 3.6, drop support for Python 3.3.\n\n## 3.1 (2016-04-03)\n\n- Add support for Python 3.4 and 3.5.\n- Drop support for Python 2.6 and 3.2.\n\n## 3.0 (2013-05-05)\n\n- Added compatibility with Python 3.2, 3.3 and PyPy using the Python\n  implementation.\n- Added a Python reference implementation of the Missing class.\n- Changed the type name of the Missing class to `Missing.Missing` to\n  distinguish it from an instance of the type like `Missing.Value`.\n\n## 2.13.1 (2010-06-16)\n\n- Added a `__class__` to Missing.Value objects.\n\n## 2.13.0 (2010-03-30)\n\n- Released as separate package.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "Missing._Missing", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "Missing", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "Missing.notMissing", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "Missing.Missing", "bases": ["Base"], "methods": [{"name": "Missing.Missing.__call__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "Missing.Missing.__repr__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "Missing.Missing.__bytes__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "Missing.Missing.__str__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "Missing.Missing.__reduce__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": n